FX Networks has made some changes to the FXNOW app as we are now part of The Walt Disney Company: NEW LOOK: Don t worry you can still watch all your favorite shows and movies live or on demand. FX ACCOUNT: Sign in to your account previously known as an FX profile to transfer your favorite shows and viewing history. TV PROVIDER: You may need to sign in to your TV provider again to watch certain videos.

The Simpsons just got bigger with the home player available in full screen! Tap for sound in Simpsons World to hear them in all their glory. Sound is off by default. Faster tablet interface with easier navigation Various bug fixes and performance upgrades

3D Touch is here! With quick home screen actions you can easily resume watching your content as well as access shows movies and even random Simpsons episodes clips. With a light touch on any of our shows a clip will auto play and a quick swipe up will allow you to play the latest episode access extras or set a reminder before the show airs. With a light touch on movies you can quickly see movie details as well as play a movie and set a reminder before its gone. Audio Commentary is now on Simpsons World. For the first time ever watch Season 18 with audio commentary and get thoughts from the writers actors directors and animators of the Simpsons.
